<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cookie Policy - Malaysia Pickleball Association</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 min-h-screen">
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>
  <%- include('../partials/sidebar') %>
  
  <main class="md:ml-64 min-h-screen relative z-10" style="padding-top: var(--navbar-height);">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Cookie Policy</h1>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Malaysia Pickleball Association</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">What Are Cookies?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Cookies are small text files that are placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit our website. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and provide information to website owners.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">How We Use Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Malaysia Pickleball Association uses cookies to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Remember your login information and preferences</li>
              <li>Analyze website traffic and user behavior</li>
              <li>Improve website functionality and user experience</li>
              <li>Provide personalized content and recommendations</li>
              <li>Enable social media features and integrations</li>
              <li>Deliver targeted advertisements and marketing content</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Essential Cookies</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly. They include:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>Session cookies for user authentication</li>
                  <li>Security cookies to prevent fraud</li>
                  <li>Load balancing cookies for website performance</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">Functional Cookies</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">These cookies enhance functionality and personalization:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>Language and region preferences</li>
                  <li>User interface customizations</li>
                  <li>Tournament and event preferences</li>
                  <li>Player dashboard settings</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-2">Analytics Cookies</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">These cookies help us understand how visitors use our website:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>Google Analytics for website statistics</li>
                  <li>Page view and session duration tracking</li>
                  <li>User journey and behavior analysis</li>
                  <li>Tournament registration conversion tracking</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-2">Marketing Cookies</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">These cookies are used for advertising and marketing purposes:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>Social media integration (Facebook, Instagram, Twitter)</li>
                  <li>Targeted advertising based on interests</li>
                  <li>Email marketing campaign tracking</li>
                  <li>Retargeting for tournament promotions</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We may also use third-party services that set cookies on our website:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website analytics and performance tracking</li>
              <li><strong>Facebook Pixel:</strong> For social media integration and advertising</li>
              <li><strong>YouTube:</strong> For embedded video content and live streaming</li>
              <li><strong>Payment Processors:</strong> For secure tournament registration payments</li>
              <li><strong>Email Services:</strong> For newsletter and communication tracking</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Technical Partnership</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              The Malaysia Pickleball Association website is developed and maintained by our Technical Partner, <strong>Fenix Digital</strong>. As part of their technical services, Fenix Digital implements and manages:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Cookie implementation and management systems</li>
              <li>Analytics and tracking code integration</li>
              <li>Third-party service integrations (Google Analytics, social media)</li>
              <li>Website performance optimization cookies</li>
              <li>Security and authentication cookies</li>
              <li>User experience enhancement features</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              All cookie implementations follow industry best practices and comply with applicable privacy regulations under Fenix Digital's technical guidance.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              You have several options for managing cookies:
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Browser Settings</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Most browsers allow you to:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <li>View and delete cookies</li>
                <li>Block cookies from specific websites</li>
                <li>Block third-party cookies</li>
                <li>Clear all cookies when you close your browser</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Opt-Out Options</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">You can opt out of specific tracking:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <li><a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Google Analytics Opt-out</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/settings?tab=ads" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Facebook Ad Preferences</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://optout.networkadvertising.org/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Network Advertising Initiative Opt-out</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Cookie Retention</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Different cookies have different retention periods:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Deleted when you close your browser</li>
              <li><strong>Persistent Cookies:</strong> Remain for a set period (typically 30 days to 2 years)</li>
              <li><strong>Authentication Cookies:</strong> Usually expire after 30 days of inactivity</li>
              <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Typically retained for 26 months</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Impact of Disabling Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              If you choose to disable cookies, some features of our website may not work properly:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>You may need to log in repeatedly</li>
              <li>Your preferences and settings may not be saved</li>
              <li>Some interactive features may not function</li>
              <li>Tournament registration may be affected</li>
              <li>Personalized content may not be available</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Updates to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or applicable laws. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated policy on our website and updating the "Last updated" date.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              If you have any questions about our use of cookies or this Cookie Policy, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
              <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Malaysia Pickleball Association</strong></p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Email: privacy@malaysiapickleball.org</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Website: www.malaysiapickleball.org</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Subject: Cookie Policy Inquiry</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
              For technical questions about cookie implementation or website functionality, please contact our Technical Partner:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Fenix Digital</strong></p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Technical Partner for Malaysia Pickleball Association</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Email: support@fenixdigital.com</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Website: www.fenixdigital.com</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Subject: Technical Support - Cookie Policy</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <!-- Back to Home Button -->
        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors duration-300">
            <i class="fas fa-home mr-2"></i>
            Back to Home
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html> 